# Buscacursos++

Esta API permite hacer un CRUD de reviews de cursos y profesores que se encuentran en una aplicación RoR.


## Colección de Reviews [/reviews]

### Lista todos los Reviews  [GET]

Queda pendiente 
+ Request (application/json)

+ Response 201 (application/json)
        
    

### Crear un nuevo review [POST]

Crea un nuevo review, adjuntando los datos del curso y el usuario en un JSON.

+ Request (application/json)
    + Headers
    
            Authorization: oauth_token
            
    + Body

            {
                "course": {
                    "name": "Desarrollo de Sofware",
                    "number": "IIC3143"
                },
                "content": "Este curso es el mejor que he tomado este semestre",
            }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

            {
                "status":"success",
                "data": 
                    {
                        "course": "Desarrollo de Sofware",
                        "number": "IIC3143",
                        "created_at": "2018-05-22T21:17:20.132Z",
                        "updated_at": "2018-05-22T21:17:20.132Z",
                        "url": "http://localhost:3000/courses/1.json",
                        "reviews": [ 
                            {
                                "id": 2,
                                "created_at": "2018-05-22T21:23:16.850Z",
                                "updated_at": "2018-05-22T21:23:16.850Z",
                                "content": "Este curso es el mejor que he tomado este semestre",
                                "url": "http://localhost:3000/reviews/2.json",
                                "author": {
                                    "first_name": "IGNACIO",
                                    "last_name": "HERMOSILLA CORNEJO",
                                    "picture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-XdUIqdMkCWA/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAAAA/4252rscbv5M/photo.jpg"
                                },
                                "like_total" : 0,
                                "like_authors": []
                            }
                        ]
                    }   
                
            }
        
+ Request Edge case (application/json)
    + Headers
    
            Authorization: oauth_token
            
    + Body

            {
                "course": {
                    "name": "Desarrollo de Sofware",
                    "number": "IIC3143"
                },
                "content": ""
            }
            
+ Response 401 (application/json)

            {
                "status": "fail",
                "data": {
                    "message": "Empty Review"
                }
            }




## Review [/review/1]


### Actualizar Review [PUT]
Edita el Texto de una review del mismo usuario
        
+ Request  (application/json)
    + Headers
    
            Authorization: oauth_token
            
    + Body

            {
                "content": "nuevo contenido para el review"
            }
            
+ Response 200 (application/json)

            {
                "status": "succes",
                "data": {
                    "id": 1,
                    "name": "Desarrollo de Software",
                    "number": "IIC3143",
                    "created_at": "2018-05-22T21:17:20.132Z",
                    "updated_at": "2018-05-22T21:17:20.132Z",
                    "url": "http://localhost:3000/courses/1",
                    "reviews": [
                        {
                            "id": 16,
                            "created_at": "2018-05-23T07:07:51.719Z",
